{"tid":878872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《向香港警察致敬》深水埗小童亂過馬路　三名警察及時趕出救人","createTime":"2018-10-27T13:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T05:31:35.000Z","uid":174420,"like":247,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"9a330061e0c857658754b65ba79c1b70d2dfa3e3","tid":878872,"uid":174420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:10:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/211041_3c2c0fc286eda7b48ed0d56603d0a833.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F211041_3c2c0fc286eda7b48ed0d56603d0a833.jpeg&h=acb11c29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深水埗荔枝角道與欽州街十字路口，交通繁忙，如不根據交通指示過馬路，分分鐘釀成悲劇。但網傳一段車Cam片段，卻見到一小童疑無視交通燈號，穿梭於馬路與汽車之間，險象橫生！<br />\n警員手急腳快抱起小童回行人路<br />\n該段片短一開始即見一名小童疑不理會交通燈號，突然橫過欽州街行人過路處，幸好當時一輛準備右轉入欽州街的貨車及時收油減慢車速，才避免撞倒小童。惟其後小童並無因此返回行人路，反而再次橫越大馬路，快步走向荔枝角道。目睹整個過程的駕駛者嬲爆怒斥：「嘩！痴X線架！」隨即響按提醒其他道路駕駛者留意小童，此時亦有三名警察邊舉手示意，邊奔出馬路，將小童抱起返回行人路。由於小童似無家人陪同亂過馬路，險釀成悲劇，大批網民看到車Cam片後怒斥小童父母「去咗邊？」，並質疑有人疏忽照顧兒童，同時大讚三個阿Sir眼明手快及時救人。"},{"pid":"4bdfbb2f1c8df63e5b8616129c1786c8c4a03f1a","tid":878872,"uid":174420,"like":22,"dislike":141,"score":-119,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:11:59.000Z","msg":"今次兒燈登冇理由反掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116290b283b61085e9f5243ecb9d6cea02bfeb77","tid":878872,"uid":174420,"like":1,"dislike":68,"score":-67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:12:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今次兒登仔冇理由反掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9f2d048b19e26d33d3184e69aba5ab19ba7d85b1","tid":878872,"uid":113626,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366c691eb27c8d93d29df6e61a55b496cd83ff36","tid":878872,"uid":113626,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過好快比150換走哂"},{"pid":"e44516560615ab20e399a6bb8ea759d1c03b3f02","tid":878872,"uid":5995,"like":41,"dislike":85,"score":-44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wbvSHud.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwbvSHud.gif&h=5b0be8ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f7a65a2a1f438113548b77769fe8a1ab5b7d873","tid":878872,"uid":45644,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:14:10.000Z","msg":"呀sir救細路唔洗你教！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebbb23ae863b361b0c1fc2e3351deffd6297314","tid":878872,"uid":45613,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:16:23.000Z","msg":"貨車佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24f1b0b35322a841082fd608c4168fe7b5e41ef","tid":878872,"uid":45185,"like":114,"dislike":5,"score":109,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:19:33.000Z","msg":"支那蝗幼蟲又贏，好心幫手滅蟲啦"},{"pid":"8c36b6e1aac3289de3594418c9fdcf0e698e398a","tid":878872,"uid":294,"like":47,"dislike":66,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:21:21.000Z","msg":"兒登仔搵緊位入，等多陣"},{"pid":"671229d1384d4cbdc9c62c5a58ab7a026a0c4fba","tid":878872,"uid":182334,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"人非草木"},{"pid":"ecb648fe1e32f998fd3af595b56196d4cd0cc4ae","tid":878872,"uid":174420,"like":3,"dislike":42,"score":-39,"quote":{"pid":"8c36b6e1aac3289de3594418c9fdcf0e698e398a","tid":878872,"uid":294,"like":47,"dislike":66,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:21:21.000Z","msg":"兒登仔搵緊位入，等多陣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:31:02.000Z","msg":"今次都搵唔到位入啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852eb40043e4dfeb1ec4ebea0a24693ace71cce1","tid":878872,"uid":73621,"like":21,"dislike":152,"score":-131,"c